      "content": "i hear you, but i just don't feel comfortable with it. my doctor was so rushed and just handed me the prescription without explaining why it has to be 10 days specifically. if i can see the skin is totally clear, how can you be so certain there's still stuff in there? it seems more logical to listen to my body than to a generic number. can't you just confirm that if there are no symptoms, the danger of stopping is actually pretty low?",
